OL,3,CMan charged with murder after death of
OL,4,C82-year-old in Camden
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Ffollowing the death of an 82-year-old
OL,8,Fman at a property in Camden.
OL,10,FMetropolitan Policer officers were
OL,11,Fcalled to a house in West End Lane,
OL,12,FNW6 at around 11:25am on Thursday 5
OL,13,FMarch.
OL,15,FUpon arrival at the property,
OL,16,Fparamedics from the London Ambulance
OL,17,FService confirmed an 82-year-old man
OL,18,Fhad died.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/2
