OL,3,CMan charged with murder after death of
OL,4,C82-year-old in Camden
OL,6,FAn arrest took place inside the house
OL,7,Fwithin minutes of police arriving, the
OL,8,FMet said.
OL,10,FBilly O'Reilly, 53, of Royal Free
OL,11,FSquare, Islington, was charged with
OL,12,Fmurder on Friday 6 March. He was due
OL,13,Fto appear at Westminster Magistrates
OL,14,FCourt on Saturday 7 March.
